{"tid":1979569,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"科大推廣文 - 你問我答 (4)","createTime":"2020-04-19T13:38:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T06:38:07.000Z","uid":78512,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"0318cff74d3e1663e3df9b2a0ca37d382676a317","tid":1979569,"uid":78512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T13:38:12.000Z","msg":"各位DSE既同學仔大家好, 唔知你地諗好入咩大學同讀咩科未呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日小妹我開呢個post就係為大家打打氣, 順便同大家介紹下科大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 科大名聲好, 排名高<br />\n科大, 別名<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Asia MIT, 香港第0</span></span><br />\n根據QS排名, 科大<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">曾經</span></span>超越港大成為左香港第0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n科大既engine同business係17年既排名更加比港大個排名高唔少<br />\n第時入到科大比d豬朋狗友問你出路, 你都絕對可以好驕傲咁講我讀科大啊, 相信唔少人都會讀你叻仔叻女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 科大學術氣氛好<br />\n大家咁辛苦入到大學梗係想追求更多既知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n科大係呢方面就訓練到學生十分著重讀書, 每星期都安排唔同既功課同測驗比學生溫故而知新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你可以見到既就係同學落堂去就擁埋去教授到問書, 問完就會去拉把溫習, 同學之間都會有各種既學術討論, 係咁既氛圍底下, 你GPA都自然會高啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 科大男女比例均衡<br />\n街外人經常流傳科大係咩少林寺啊, 格劍聖地等<br />\n呢d其實都係唔太正確既講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以business school為例, 16intake男女比例為<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">47:53</span></span>, 53既仲要係女黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試想像下上堂acct堂, 前後左右都係女既話, 你每堂都有動力去上啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSource:<a href=\"http://undergrad.bm.ust.hk/eng/why/students/our_students/index.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fundergrad.bm.ust.hk%2Feng%2Fwhy%2Fstudents%2Four_students%2Findex.jsp&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWpFDRn80AWZfiUxX1c6OkmY%3D&h=bdadc8ec\" target=\"_blank\">http://undergrad.bm.ust.hk/eng/why/students/our_students/index.jsp</a><br />\n<br />\n再聽下幾個名人分享科大:<br />\n1. 嶺大分數, 三大名氣/engine就是ust(鍵盤騎士, 2015) <br />\n相信大家都聽過呢類型既說話, 想用大學黎證明自己能力, 科大絕對係你既首選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 港大張xx/鏗x都同鍵騎有唔少交情, 佢地都好支持鍵騎入讀科大civil, 認為係明智之選<br />\n<br />\n各位DSE同學仔聽完係咪心動呢, 如果係就請立即登入JUPAS Account, 更改你既選擇至JS5xxxx (任何你心儀既科大科目)<br />\n祝福你地DSE都能順利渡過, 9月係科大呢個大家庭見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b6d8c82082de60f4082a34380bd51a5932d661","tid":1979569,"uid":3380,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T14:49:10.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong University of Sunshine and Tomorrow <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173527e3117baead41f8584132fb9ec8d788fd64","tid":1979569,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T14:57:28.000Z","msg":"4.科大女仔特別怕羞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n讀左差唔多成年 一條女都識唔到on99"},{"pid":"e1305917bf6ab4eb2e37358f4171331dcbc097ad","tid":1979569,"uid":108548,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T15:05:01.000Z","msg":"唔好聽樓主講啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 身邊有好多人讀到好大壓力<br />\n成日都話好chur好chur  真係睇人 我就讀得幾開心嘅   如果你抗壓 自學能力極高 咁科大都叫做喺唔錯嘅選擇  如果唔受得壓就真係第間啦 你會想死<br />\n利申：科大year4"},{"pid":"4fca2ae604b64b089a3088997fde794be42dce6e","tid":1979569,"uid":108548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1305917bf6ab4eb2e37358f4171331dcbc097ad","tid":1979569,"uid":108548,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T15:05:01.000Z","msg":"唔好聽樓主講啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 身邊有好多人讀到好大壓力<br />\n成日都話好chur好chur  真係睇人 我就讀得幾開心嘅   如果你抗壓 自學能力極高 咁科大都叫做喺唔錯嘅選